Papa's Freezeria is a delightful time management and simulation game that allows players to run their own ice cream shop. Developed by Flipline Studios, this popular game invites players to step into the shoes of a budding entrepreneur and master the art of crafting delicious frozen treats. Get ready to serve up smiles and satisfy your customers' sweet cravings in Papa's Freezeria!
